01:44.905 --> 01:46.304
He birdies here,

01:46.306 --> 01:48.607
he walks away
with the Green Jacket.

01:48.609 --> 01:50.208
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(HORN HONKING)</font></b>
- Fuck!

01:52.379 --> 01:54.546
Wonderful.

02:12.499 --> 02:14.366
You're late.

02:14.368 --> 02:17.269
<b><font color="#D900D9">(SPEAKING SPANISH)</font></b>

02:27.648 --> 02:30.949
- The weapons?
- It's on the boat. The cash?

02:34.187 --> 02:37.022
- Feels a little light.
- That's 45,000 now.

02:37.024 --> 02:39.190
