02:51.071 --> 02:52.604
<b><font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font></b>

02:52.606 --> 02:54.940
Okay. Fine.

02:54.942 --> 02:57.409
You want to play games?
I'll play games.

02:57.411 --> 02:59.978
