Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

03:29.343 --> 03:31.042
- Wait!
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font></b>

03:34.414 --> 03:38.350
Ryan, get the bags,
get the weapons.

03:38.352 --> 03:42.187
<b><font color="#D900D9">(GROANS, SIGHS)</font></b>

03:45.292 --> 03:47.192
Not cool,<i> hombre.</i>

03:52.466 --> 03:53.531
<b><font color="#D900D9">(GASPS)</font></b>

03:56.103 --> 03:58.103
I can do this
all day,<i> amigo.</i>

03:58.105 --> 03:59.571
Fuck!

04:01.341 --> 04:02.440
- Oh, shit.
- Blanks.

04:02.442 --> 04:04.743
Logan. Logan. Logan.

04:04.745 --> 04:07.145
- Logan!
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(SPEAKING SPANISH)</font></b>

04:07.147 --> 04:09.447
Logan. Logan!

04:10.150 --> 04:11.416
Logan!

04:12.519 --> 04:14.519
<b><font color="#D900D9">(MAN SHOUTS IN SPANISH)</font></b>

04:25.665 --> 04:27.198
<b><font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font></b>

04:27.200 --> 04:29.434
<b><font color="#D900D9">(GROANS, SIGHS)</font></b>

04:32.506 --> 04:36.474
Well, this is a sad commentary
on today's society.

04:36.476 --> 04:39.811
<b><font color="#808080">LOGAN:</font></b> <b><font color="#D900D9">(OVER EARPIECE)</font></b>
<i>Don't take it too personal, Jack.</i>

04:39.813 --> 04:43.081
Don't kid yourself, partner.
It's always personal.

04:43.083 --> 04:45.250
PS, where the fuck
were you on those last two?

04:45.252 --> 04:49.054
Marksmanship 101, boss.
Gun-target line was shit.

04:49.056 --> 04:51.523
I'm firing .308 win mags.

04:51.525 --> 04:54.492
Oh, by the way,
you got some brain in your hair.

04:54.494 --> 04:58.463
- Jesus Christ!
<i>- At this range, a .308 woulda ripped right through</i>

04:58.465 --> 05:03.068
your recently deceased business partners
and left you with a sucking chest wound.

05:03.070 --> 05:06.204
Well, good to know. All right,
let's get the hell out of here.

05:06.206 --> 05:08.139
On my way, boss man.

05:18.185 --> 05:19.384
<b><font color="#808080">JACK:</font></b> What happened
with Gabriel's rounds?

05:19.386 --> 05:21.419
I couldn't get
to his spare mags.

05:21.421 --> 05:24.456
- He would have noticed!
- That could have been bad.

05:24.458 --> 05:27.826
- Could have.
- You guys are fucking idiots, by the way.

05:27.828 --> 05:31.563
How many more times you think you're
going to get away with this blanks shit?

05:31.565 --> 05:33.565
Is that concern
I hear in your voice?

05:33.567 --> 05:36.134
Yeah, concern
for my future employment.

05:36.136 --> 05:40.572
My skill set doesn't exactly
translate to working at Starbucks.

05:40.574 --> 05:43.475
Let's get out of here.

05:43.477 --> 05:44.876
I'll see you
in a couple of weeks.

05:44.878 --> 05:46.444
If you're lucky.

05:46.446 --> 05:49.414
Come on, let's see what you got.
Come on. There you go.

05:49.416 --> 05:52.283
Hey, hey, hey.
Don't push me too hard.

05:52.285 --> 05:54.819
<b><font color="#D900D9">(ROCK MUSIC PLAYS)</font></b>

09:00.907 --> 09:03.508
