- Jenna would be pissed.

09:26.099 --> 09:30.968
- Jenna and me have only...
- Jenna and I. I'm just saying.

09:30.970 --> 09:34.772
Jenna and I have only
been dating for a few weeks.

09:34.774 --> 09:38.876
- I'm throwing this out.
- Fine. I don't care. Throw it out.

09:46.653 --> 09:49.921
Wow. I'm impressed.

09:49.923 --> 09:52.690
When's the last time
you heard from her, anyway?

09:52.692 --> 09:55.393
I don't know.

09:58.665 --> 10:00.665
Six months.

10:19.953 --> 10:23.388
You're a real nutless wonder,
you know that, Jack?

10:24.891 --> 10:28.025
Honestly. What the hell
did you ever see in her?

10:29.763 --> 10:33.431
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(MAN SPEAKING SPANISH)</font></b>
- <b><font color="#808080">MAN #2:</font></b> Everybody down!

10:33.433 --> 10:37.969
- <b><font color="#808080">MAN #3:</font></b> Get that. Let's go!
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(MAN SPEAKING SPANISH)</font></b>

10:37.971 --> 10:39.771
<b><font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGS)</font></b>

10:39.773 --> 10:42.573
- Hello, Edward.
- <i>So glad you picked up.</i>

10:42.575 --> 10:44.442
I'm kind of in the middle
of something right now,

10:44.444 --> 10:46.144
<i>so I'll probably
just call you back.</i>

10:46.146 --> 10:48.546
I know where you are
and I know what you are doing.

10:48.548 --> 10:49.881
<i>Or did you forget who planned</i>

10:49.883 --> 10:51.849
<i>this little trip
in the first place?</i>

10:51.851 --> 10:53.751
You called this job off, Eddie.

10:53.753 --> 10:55.853
So you can't blame me
for going ahead with this.

10:55.855 --> 10:58.689
But I do blame you. You're
doing a job that I planned.

10:58.691 --> 11:01.826
A job that I set up.
There are finder's fees associated with it.

11:01.828 --> 11:04.796
Your job you called off and I
decided to move forward with?

11:04.798 --> 11:08.866
Without me.
Without my permission, Karen.

11:08.868 --> 11:11.002
What do you want, Eddie?

11:11.004 --> 11:12.737
- My full share.
- <i>Which is?</i>

11:12.739 --> 11:15.873
- One hundred percent.
- What happened to 60?

11:15.875 --> 11:19.610
Well, the additional 40 is for the
indignity that I have suffered.

11:19.612 --> 11:22.480
- No fucking way.
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font></b>

11:22.482 --> 11:25.917
<i>Yes fucking way, Karen.</i>

11:25.919 --> 11:27.885
You called the cops?

11:27.887 --> 11:29.787
What can I say?
My feelings were hurt.

11:29.789 --> 11:31.889
<i>- You'll get nothing.
- A price I would gladly pay</i>

11:31.891 --> 11:34.625
to teach you
a long overdue lesson.

11:34.627 --> 11:38.930
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(SHOUTING)</font></b>
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOTS)</font></b>

11:44.237 --> 11:46.804
Now, Glenn,

11:46.806 --> 11:49.807
why is it that these ties look
like they were dipped in shit?

11:49.809 --> 11:54.679
- Shit, Mr. Filosa?
- Shit. Yes.

11:54.681 --> 11:56.848
Sir, you asked
for Scarlet Forest,

11:56.850 --> 11:58.783
and I assure you these ties
are all Scarlet Forest.

11:58.785 --> 12:00.885
- You're assuring me that?
- Yes, sir.

12:00.887 --> 12:04.789
I'm assuring you that they look
like they were dipped in shit.

12:07.827 --> 12:10.628
See this?

12:10.630 --> 12:15.666
See this color? When that dries, that's
the color I want on these ties.

12:15.668 --> 12:18.870
- Yes, sir.
- Off you go.

12:22.909 --> 12:28.846
If Karen makes it out alive, she'll have
no choice but to take her original flight.

12:28.848 --> 12:31.249
I need to know
exactly what she knows.

12:31.251 --> 12:33.551
Yes, sir.

12:35.855 --> 12:38.990
It's only a matter
of days now.

12:38.992 --> 12:43.160
This job,
my job is right out there.

12:43.162 --> 12:46.631
We can't let Karen fuck it up.

12:53.973 --> 12:57.174
- Absolutely fucking not.
- Why not?

12:57.176 --> 13:01.979
Why? 'Cause the fact that you borrow my dog in
order to trick your veterinarian girlfriend

13:01.981 --> 13:04.015
to thinking you're
an animal lover is pathetic.

13:04.017 --> 13:07.318
I am an animal lover,
I'm just not an animal owner.

13:07.320 --> 13:10.888
- Do you even like this woman?
- Yes, I like this woman. I like her a lot.

13:10.890 --> 13:13.591
Then why do you continue
to lie to her?

13:13.593 --> 13:15.927
I lie to her
because I like her!

13:15.929 --> 13:19.030
Ha. Well,
spoken like a true man.

13:21.000 --> 13:22.833
Stop it.

13:26.039 --> 13:29.574
