13:42.355 --> 13:46.190
- Let's go. Come on.
- Oh. And daisies are her favorites.

13:46.192 --> 13:50.895
- You know, for next time. <b><font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font></b>
- Now you tell me.

13:53.766 --> 13:56.734
