I knew you would.

14:28.635 --> 14:30.901
- How about dinner tonight?
- Hmm... two conditions.

14:30.903 --> 14:32.069
- Name them.
- You cook.

14:32.071 --> 14:34.405
- Done.
- And Grace is there.

14:34.407 --> 14:36.073
<b><font color="#808080">JACK:</font></b> Of course.
Grace will always be there.

14:36.075 --> 14:38.042
- Hi, baby. Hi!
- Who's that, Grace?

14:43.082 --> 14:45.049
<b><font color="#D900D9">(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)</font></b>

14:47.120 --> 14:50.421
