16:38.231 --> 16:41.165
<b><font color="#D900D9">(LINE RINGING)</font></b>

16:42.401 --> 16:45.970
<b><font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGS)</font></b>

16:45.972 --> 16:48.239
- Yeah.
- <b><font color="#808080">MAN:</font></b> <i>I found them, sir.</i>

16:48.241 --> 16:49.907
- Good.
- <i>They'll be dead by morning.</i>

16:49.909 --> 16:52.309
- Finish it.
- <i>Yes, sir.</i>

17:17.970 --> 17:21.806
- How many months?
- Got any pickles?

17:21.808 --> 17:26.076
- Karen...
- It's yours.

17:27.814 --> 17:31.549
I know. I was in denial too
for a little while.

17:31.551 --> 17:34.084
It's the first
of five stages of grief.

17:34.086 --> 17:35.953
- Then there is...
- Where the fuck have you been?!

17:35.955 --> 17:38.289
Then there's anger.

17:38.291 --> 17:41.158
- I'm going to go.
- Oh! Jenna... Jenna.

17:41.160 --> 17:44.862
Jenna, please, I'm so sorry
about this, you know... I...

17:44.864 --> 17:47.565
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font></b>
- Grace! Please!

17:47.567 --> 17:49.166
- Do you want to call me later?
- Yes, of course.

17:49.168 --> 17:52.102
Gimme a second.
Grace. Grace, knock it off!

17:52.104 --> 17:54.505
I'm sorry. Just give me
one second, I'll walk you...

17:54.507 --> 17:58.175
Grace! Come on, girl. Shut up!

18:00.179 --> 18:02.346
<b><font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font></b>

18:02.348 --> 18:04.849
Oh, shit!

18:06.953 --> 18:09.486
Jenna, I need you
to listen to me.

18:09.488 --> 18:11.455
Something very dangerous
is about to happen.

18:11.457 --> 18:14.525
You can not ask any questions.
Do you understand me?

18:14.527 --> 18:16.260
- What?
- That was a question!

18:16.262 --> 18:20.431
<b><font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font></b>

