18:55.234 --> 18:57.468
- You and me are going to talk.
- Now?

18:57.470 --> 19:00.304
- Get to the boat.
- Let's go.

19:13.286 --> 19:16.287
<b><font color="#D900D9">(BANGING)</font></b>

19:28.701 --> 19:31.402
- Move! Move! Move!
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(JENNA SCREAMS)</font></b>

19:32.605 --> 19:34.939
Let's go! Come on,
Jenna, get in the boat!

19:40.313 --> 19:41.445
Come on, girl! Let's go!

19:41.447 --> 19:42.680
<b><font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font></b>

19:44.417 --> 19:46.216
- Karen, get down!
- The dock!

19:47.053 --> 19:49.420
Move, move, move!

19:56.262 --> 19:57.294
Get on the boat!

20:26.625 --> 20:29.293
- <b><font color="#808080">KAREN:</font></b> Jack!
- Give me a minute, Karen.

20:29.295 --> 20:31.261
- Yeah, but I...
- Did you see the finger?!

20:31.263 --> 20:33.163
- Yes, Jack, I see the finger!
- Well, the finger means

20:33.165 --> 20:37.067
- I need one minute to think!
- Here they come!

20:41.040 --> 20:43.007
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(PHONE DIALING)</font></b>
- What are you doing?

20:43.009 --> 20:45.376
- I'm calling the police!
- Give me that!

20:45.378 --> 20:47.378
There's no calling the police!

20:53.352 --> 20:54.651
Ah!

20:59.025 --> 21:03.227
- Where are we going, Jack?
- Somewhere safe, Jenna.

21:05.297 --> 21:08.599
- Okay, Karen, go.
- Someone thinks I stole from him.

21:08.601 --> 21:11.201
- Did you? Karen!
- What?!

21:11.203 --> 21:14.038
- Did you steal from someone?
- No!

21:14.040 --> 21:17.541
Jesus Christ! Do you ever
think anything through?!

21:17.543 --> 21:21.512
Oh, don't talk to me about thinking things
through! You over analyze everything!

21:21.514 --> 21:24.815
I like to plan! I like to plan so I don't
get into shit like this!

21:24.817 --> 21:29.486
Please just pay attention to
the people trying to kill us!

21:29.488 --> 21:30.788
Faster! Faster! Let's go!

21:33.259 --> 21:35.826
- I ran a job for Eddie Filosa.
- Oh, mistake number one.

21:35.828 --> 21:38.095
- You know him?
- I know of him.

21:40.232 --> 21:42.533
Well, the job went south
and we lost the score.

21:42.535 --> 21:44.234
Well, that happens.

21:46.472 --> 21:49.640
Yeah, well, tell that to Eddie.
He wants me to make good for it!

21:51.377 --> 21:53.544
- All of it?
- All of it!

21:57.416 --> 21:59.650
- How big?
- Huge!

21:59.652 --> 22:03.487
- That's not very rational.
- Eddie's not exactly rational, Jack.

22:07.493 --> 22:08.659
<b><font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font></b>

22:08.661 --> 22:11.495
- Is she okay?
- She's fine.

22:11.497 --> 22:15.833
- What is Logan's dog even doing here?
- Grace is Logan's dog?

22:15.835 --> 22:18.702
- She didn't know?
- I was going to tell you.

22:18.704 --> 22:21.271
- <b><font color="#D900D9">(KAREN LAUGHS)</font></b>
- You were going to tell me what part, Jack?

22:21.273 --> 22:24.308
That Grace isn't yours,
that you got an ex-girlfriend pregnant,

22:24.310 --> 22:26.577
or that you're some type
of uber-criminal?!

22:26.579 --> 22:29.213
She's got a point, Jack.

22:31.750 --> 22:34.852
Come on, faster! Go!

22:41.594 --> 22:43.594
Can you take out that Jet Ski?

22:43.596 --> 22:46.497
I'm out! Of course
I can take out the Jet Ski!

22:52.438 --> 22:54.738
There's something wrong
with your gun!

22:54.740 --> 22:56.473
There's nothing wrong
with my gun, Karen.

22:56.475 --> 22:58.142
Oh, really?

22:58.144 --> 23:00.177
Then why don't we let "this
year's model" give it a try?

23:00.179 --> 23:03.914
- Just leave her alone.
- Why? I know she likes to just lay on her back,

23:03.916 --> 23:05.716
but maybe she wants
to participate more.

23:05.718 --> 23:08.452
What the hell did you ever see
in this woman, Jack?

23:08.454 --> 23:11.522
I gave him a reason
to fuck with the lights on!

23:21.567 --> 23:23.267
- Jack!
- What?

23:23.269 --> 23:24.668
<b><font color="#808080">KAREN:</font></b> There are
no more Jet Skis.

23:24.670 --> 23:26.737
The bad news, no more guns.

23:26.739 --> 23:29.840
